Run an HTTP server using Go's standard library

Usage:
  llm-proxy run server [flags]

Flags:
  -h, --help                   help for server
      --ollama-url string      Upstream Ollama URL (default "http://localhost:11434")
      --port int               Port to listen on (default 11435)
      --wandb-api-key string   W&B API key for Weave tracing (env: WANDB_API_KEY)
      --wandb-project string   W&B project for Weave tracing, format: entity/project (env: WANDB_PROJECT)

Global Flags:
      --log-format string   Log format: text, json (default: text if interactive, json otherwise)
      --log-level string    Log level: debug, info, warn, error (default "info")
